content.body: does https://github.com/w3c/webidl2.js have its own discord/slack/matrix or is here fine? ive been working an a new parser implementation and using their test suite as a reference along with the spec. however it seems a number of cases are out of date? I didnt know if this is something they were aware of or if we should coordinate it or a bunch of small prs would be best
I'm not aware of any specific community for that library.
Meghan Denny: As far as chat, here seems probably like the best place. krosylight is here — along with others who might make time to pitch in on updating the tests
